 What is the periodization of these historical moments

358
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:26,000
 in which Ross studies Augustine?

359
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:31,000
 There are the times of forties of Constantinople.

360
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:36,000
 We have the Union of Florence, Mark of Ephesus,

361
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:44,000
 and also we have some modern issues.

362
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:51,000
 It is very interesting that all three authors speak about Nicodemus

363
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:56,000
 from the Holy Mountain.

