00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:12,000
 They all speak about Nicodemus and they want to put--

366
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:19,000
 to speak about necessity to venerate Augustine

367
00:39:19,000 --> 00:39:26,000
 in their particular private piety.

