00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:24,000
 It was probably Martin Luther who first discovered

381
00:40:24,000 --> 00:40:28,000
 that this doctrine contradicted Augustine's theology.

382
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:32,000
 Seraphim Rose doesn't know about it.

383
00:40:32,000 --> 00:40:36,000
 He doesn't know probably that Luther called it "Semi-Pelagianism"

384
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:39,000
 and accused the modern Catholic Church of holding it,

385
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:43,000
 that is, in his opinion, of being in heresy.

386
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:46,000
 This brief information is given here only as an excursion.

